title: Best Bits of the Week with Morgan2 - What You Didn't Hear About Our Breakfast Food Debate + Getting to Know Members of the Show (Week of 2/8)
itunes:title: Best Bits of the Week with Morgan2 - What You Didn't Hear About Our Breakfast Food Debate + Getting to Know Members of the Show (Week of 2/8)
description:
This edition of the podcast features behind the scenes from show members and moments that happened after we turned off the microphones. Morgan2 brings on Eddie, Lunchbox, Raymundo, Scuba Steve, Hillary and Abby to talk about their favorite breakfast foods like we did on the show earlier this week.
